    <h3>The <em>Opportunity</em></h3>
    <p>Risk modeling has made essential progress in the last two decades. While no model can ever fully represent the dynamic nature and complexity of the real world, today's models are highly sophisticated tools that provide a wealth of understanding and insight. And yet, we could do so much more.</p>
    <p>Critical advances in analytic and technical computing in recent years are making it possible to push beyond the conventional limitations of modeling&mdash;but only if we take a fundamental step forward together. Inspired by the potential for powerful infrastructure improvement and greater freedom of innovation, RMS is committed to helping our industry realize the benefits of advanced computing technology through an entirely new modeling and analytic platform that will tap the cloud to deliver universal high-performance computing.</p>
    <p>Enabled by next generation computing technology, tomorrow's models will be faster, more complete, and dramatically easier to run, adapt, and interpret. Supported by a new RMS platform, they'll be fully integrated in business operations to enable truly informed business decisions based on risk exposure analysis in real time. Beyond improved and more efficient risk quantification, tomorrow's solutions will deliver risk intelligence with the power to improve business performance.</p>
