    <h4>Make today's decisions based on today's risk</h4>
    <p>No longer a separate silo, the RMS platform will enable modeling and risk information to be efficiently embedded in the underwriting and portfolio management workflow. Businesses will monitor their portfolios dynamically and in real time, not based on data that is weeks or months old. Eliminating this lag in information will enable more efficient management of business capital and capacity and make modeling and risk management an integral and auditable part of the core business process.</p>
  </section>

