    <p>Every major catastrophe reveals how much we still have to learn about risk. No single group of modelers, no matter how well resourced, can provide all the insights for such a vast and uncertain environment as the world we live in. Even in developed markets where more established models already exist, there remains room for more nuanced understanding of catastrophe risk. Meeting today's challenges requires the insight and expertise of the entire risk modeling community.</p>
    <p>The new platform is an open ecosystem&mdash;a platform that is open to the best, and delivers mission-critical insight at the heart of the enterprise. From catastrophe models to underwriting models, it will support our applications, your applications, and even their applications.</p>
